### ---------------------------------------------------------
### 1) Add EXPENSE transaction
### ---------------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "expense",
  "category": "Travel",
  "amount": 400.0,
  "date": "2025-12-22"
}

### Expected Response (200 OK)
#{
#  "type": "expense",
#  "category": "Travel",
#  "amount": 400.0,
#  "date": "2025-12-22",
#  "id": 1
#}
#id marks how many times you test the endpoint

